  "title": "*NEW* 6 months Contract Events Management (Banking) $4,000 to S$5,500 #NJA",
  "description": "<p><strong>The Job: </strong></p><ul><li>Develop and manage the company’s social impact programmes which align with  Group’s sustainability focus and commitments </li><li>Overseeing the company volunteering activities and fund-raising initiatives</li><li>Initiate and develop collaborations with relevant government agencies, non-profit\norganizations, and other community stakeholders, to achieve desired outcomes and impact.</li><li>Work with internal committee to drive volunteer engagement and recognition, to sustain high  levels of employee participation. </li><li>Collaborate closely with stakeholders to drive external and internal communication to raise awareness on social impact topics, programmes and events.</li><li>Offer expertise, guidance and collaboration with business units on social impact related campaigns and programme</li></ul><p><strong>Interested applicants can send their detailed resumes to </strong><a href=\"mailto:janelui@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">janelui@recruitexpress.com.sg </a><strong>or call JANE @ 6735 1955. </strong></p><p><strong>JANE LUI JIE'EN </strong></p><p><strong>CEI: R1104482</strong></p><p><u><strong>Company Reg. No. 199601303W || EA Licence No. 99C4599</strong></u><br /></p>",
